00:34:48.230 --> 00:34:49.150
Grandpa,

00:34:49.380 --> 00:34:50.000
I advise you

00:34:50.000 --> 00:34:51.030
to step aside.

00:34:51.389 --> 00:34:51.900
If your family

00:34:51.900 --> 00:34:53.030
had any strong connections,

00:34:53.030 --> 00:34:53.500
I wouldn't be

00:34:53.500 --> 00:34:54.699
standing here today.

00:34:55.730 --> 00:34:56.340
Guys.

00:34:57.050 --> 00:34:58.550
Get to work. Push.

00:34:58.940 --> 00:34:59.800
Don't you dare.

00:34:59.940 --> 00:35:00.380
Move aside!

00:35:00.380 --> 00:35:01.110
Don't fight!

00:35:01.690 --> 00:35:02.230
Move!

00:35:02.420 --> 00:35:03.380
Zhacuo! Zhacuo!

00:35:03.400 --> 00:35:03.990
Get back!

00:35:04.030 --> 00:35:04.830
Let go! Let go!

00:35:05.010 --> 00:35:05.780
Back off!

00:35:06.470 --> 00:35:06.870
Let go!

00:35:06.890 --> 00:35:08.020
-Move!
-Stop! Stop!

00:35:10.870 --> 00:35:11.470
Chairman.

00:35:11.500 --> 00:35:12.430
Why are you here?

00:35:17.130 --> 00:35:18.460
Don't worry, Chairman.

00:35:18.500 --> 00:35:20.300
I've arranged everything here.

00:35:22.300 --> 00:35:23.010
Mayor Lin.

00:35:23.910 --> 00:35:24.750
I'm late.

00:35:32.060 --> 00:35:33.330
You are a bit late.

00:35:35.070 --> 00:35:36.730
Is this how

00:35:38.680 --> 00:35:40.940
Xinhai's integration operations work?

00:35:42.800 --> 00:35:43.670
Is this what you call

00:35:43.670 --> 00:35:45.070
social responsibility?

00:35:47.010 --> 00:35:48.140
I am terribly sorry.

00:35:48.300 --> 00:35:49.850
It is my management failure.

00:35:49.850 --> 00:35:51.310
I'll handle it right away.

00:35:57.730 --> 00:35:58.930
You called them here.

00:36:05.630 --> 00:36:06.560
Drive them back.

00:36:07.270 --> 00:36:07.850
Okay.

00:36:13.360 --> 00:36:14.700
Who asked you to meddle?

00:36:14.880 --> 00:36:16.510
Who gave you permission to go?

00:36:16.510 --> 00:36:17.170
If it weren't for

00:36:17.170 --> 00:36:18.760
Meng Yaohui telling me today,

00:36:18.760 --> 00:36:19.650
about this matter,

00:36:19.650 --> 00:36:20.550
how would you end it?

00:36:20.550 --> 00:36:22.070
I'm asking you, how would you fix it?

00:36:22.070 --> 00:36:23.900
Do you have a brain?

00:36:24.530 --> 00:36:26.230
Why didn't you check before acting

00:36:26.230 --> 00:36:27.630
whose pasture that was?

00:36:27.660 --> 00:36:29.000
That belongs to Duojie,

00:36:29.590 --> 00:36:31.320
Lin Peisheng's old colleague.

00:36:32.110 --> 00:36:33.260
Lin Peisheng,

00:36:33.900 --> 00:36:35.030
the Vice Mayor of Tianduo.

00:36:35.030 --> 00:36:36.430
You don't recognize him,

00:36:36.670 --> 00:36:38.330
and even called him "Old Man"?

00:36:38.680 --> 00:36:41.140
I think you are the one
acting like a big shot.

00:36:47.430 --> 00:36:49.200
No one told me who he was.

00:36:50.320 --> 00:36:51.590
He is the Mayor.

00:36:51.610 --> 00:36:53.070
He's on the news every day.

00:36:53.340 --> 00:36:55.050
You're uneducated and don't read papers.

00:36:55.050 --> 00:36:56.580
Can't you at least watch TV?

00:36:58.730 --> 00:37:00.380
Regarding the pasture integration,

00:37:00.380 --> 00:37:02.240
why I didn't let you get involved,

00:37:02.250 --> 00:37:03.680
don't you have a clue?

00:37:07.500 --> 00:37:09.130
I was afraid you'd be brainless

00:37:09.130 --> 00:37:10.460
and screw this up for me.

00:37:10.880 --> 00:37:11.670
But you just rushed in

00:37:11.670 --> 00:37:13.000
to cause trouble for me.

00:37:18.570 --> 00:37:19.340
Chairman.

00:37:20.800 --> 00:37:21.900
I handled it wrong.

00:37:24.010 --> 00:37:24.730
I was just anxious

00:37:24.730 --> 00:37:25.930
to share your burden.

00:37:27.190 --> 00:37:28.760
Then regarding that piece of land,

00:37:28.760 --> 00:37:30.290
how do you plan to handle it?

00:37:31.630 --> 00:37:32.460
Handle what?

00:37:33.360 --> 00:37:34.340
What is there to handle?

00:37:34.340 --> 00:37:35.430
I want to handle you.

00:37:35.430 --> 00:37:36.690
Can we touch that land?

00:37:37.170 --> 00:37:38.570
That land is off-limits.

00:37:39.300 --> 00:37:40.380
Idiot.

00:37:44.820 --> 00:37:45.570
You...

00:37:46.070 --> 00:37:47.780
even though you are the Vice President,

00:37:47.780 --> 00:37:48.830
if it's not your business,

00:37:48.830 --> 00:37:49.890
just stay out of it.

00:37:50.230 --> 00:37:50.630
Yes.

00:37:51.190 --> 00:37:52.100
Go back and handle the mess

00:37:52.100 --> 00:37:53.250
at Mine No. 2.

00:37:53.610 --> 00:37:54.010
Yes.

00:37:54.110 --> 00:37:55.130
If something like this

00:37:55.130 --> 00:37:56.050
happens again,

00:37:56.150 --> 00:37:56.780
you...

00:37:57.350 --> 00:37:58.690
why don't you be the Chairman?

00:37:58.690 --> 00:37:59.550
Please, don't.

00:38:00.630 --> 00:38:02.090
We wouldn't dare.

00:38:11.890 --> 00:38:12.450
Hello?

00:38:15.420 --> 00:38:15.940
Yes.

00:38:16.980 --> 00:38:18.840
I've already taught him a lesson.

00:38:19.590 --> 00:38:20.480
Don't worry.

00:38:21.230 --> 00:38:22.090
I'll have someone

00:38:22.090 --> 00:38:23.840
finalize the contract immediately.

00:38:23.840 --> 00:38:24.780
The old contract

00:38:24.840 --> 00:38:25.550
is void.

00:38:27.230 --> 00:38:27.820
No one will

00:38:27.820 --> 00:38:28.880
bother them again.

