To thank everyone,

00:38:36.540 --> 00:38:37.600
this meal is on him.

00:38:37.910 --> 00:38:39.510
So you're not the one paying.

00:38:40.570 --> 00:38:41.110
It's just a meal.

00:38:41.110 --> 00:38:42.510
No need to be this happy.

00:38:42.650 --> 00:38:43.310
Spit it out.

00:38:43.320 --> 00:38:44.010
What else?

00:38:45.210 --> 00:38:46.280
Tashi also said,

00:38:46.840 --> 00:38:47.970
to thank me,

00:38:48.590 --> 00:38:49.470
he waived my

00:38:49.500 --> 00:38:51.360
pasture contract fees for a year.

00:38:52.150 --> 00:38:53.280
What did you do

00:38:53.310 --> 00:38:54.730
to get your fees waived?

00:38:55.610 --> 00:38:56.730
If not for my buns,

00:38:57.230 --> 00:38:58.630
President Meng wouldn't have changed his mind.

00:38:58.630 --> 00:38:59.210
Right?

00:38:59.300 --> 00:38:59.940
Right.

