Come on.

00:39:01.610 --> 00:39:02.070
Come on.

00:39:02.690 --> 00:39:03.510
Let's have a drink.

00:39:03.510 --> 00:39:03.920
Old Han.

00:39:03.920 --> 00:39:04.400
Come on.

00:39:08.610 --> 00:39:09.570
Let's eat.

00:39:14.230 --> 00:39:15.290
What are you doing?

00:39:42.630 --> 00:39:44.230
About what happened before.

00:39:44.430 --> 00:39:46.160
You don't have to agree with me.

00:39:46.720 --> 00:39:47.460
But

00:39:47.920 --> 00:39:49.370
I'll keep doing it.

00:39:51.290 --> 00:39:52.820
If you cause trouble again,

00:39:53.420 --> 00:39:54.680
I'll arrest you again.

00:40:01.360 --> 00:40:01.920
Thanks.

00:40:02.380 --> 00:40:03.110
For what?

00:40:03.940 --> 00:40:04.820
As for the pasture,

00:40:04.820 --> 00:40:06.280
you don't need to thank me.

00:40:09.960 --> 00:40:11.890
That pasture belongs to everyone.

00:40:12.880 --> 00:40:13.360
Right.

