during yard time,

00:40:49.520 --> 00:40:51.190
guess who I met.

00:40:53.350 --> 00:40:53.980
Weren't you

00:40:53.980 --> 00:40:55.100
with me every day?

00:40:55.730 --> 00:40:56.960
After six months,

00:40:57.110 --> 00:40:57.880
you and Zhacuo

00:40:57.880 --> 00:41:00.080
were transferred to the Second Prison.

00:41:00.910 --> 00:41:02.020
So, who did you see?

00:41:03.430 --> 00:41:04.790
Ma Yizhong.

00:41:04.920 --> 00:41:05.760
Ma Yizhong.

00:41:06.350 --> 00:41:07.410
Why is it you again?

00:41:12.770 --> 00:41:13.520
He recognized me

00:41:13.520 --> 00:41:14.680
right away.

00:41:16.230 --> 00:41:17.480
He ran up to me

00:41:18.950 --> 00:41:20.470
and said one thing.

00:41:24.900 --> 00:41:26.900
"You're getting what you deserve."

00:41:34.570 --> 00:41:36.320
Then he just stared at me,

00:41:38.100 --> 00:41:39.790
without saying another word.

00:41:40.400 --> 00:41:41.460
Since then,

00:41:42.630 --> 00:41:43.780
whenever we met,

00:41:44.400 --> 00:41:46.130
he'd look at me from a distance,

00:41:47.150 --> 00:41:49.360
shake his head, and walk away.

00:41:52.070 --> 00:41:53.090
That felt

00:41:55.420 --> 00:41:57.420
worse than a beating.

00:42:04.860 --> 00:42:06.190
At that time, I thought,

00:42:08.130 --> 00:42:08.990
after I got out,

00:42:09.280 --> 00:42:11.240
I had to find the Captain

00:42:12.440 --> 00:42:13.460
and ask him

00:42:14.930 --> 00:42:17.450
if what we did was right.

00:42:22.720 --> 00:42:23.820
It's been 17 years.

00:42:24.520 --> 00:42:26.520
From the airport to the county town,

00:42:28.460 --> 00:42:29.990
I know every step by heart.

00:42:31.610 --> 00:42:33.810
I've been looking for him day and night.

00:42:35.920 --> 00:42:38.480
Why can't I find Captain?

00:42:45.330 --> 00:42:46.660
Are you done searching?

00:42:51.030 --> 00:42:52.490
I should be done this year.

00:42:54.460 --> 00:42:55.620
Didn't you say last year

00:42:55.620 --> 00:42:56.680
that you'd be done?

00:43:00.690 --> 00:43:02.660
I'm afraid if I finish this year,

00:43:04.740 --> 00:43:05.540
I won't know

00:43:05.570 --> 00:43:06.860
what to do with myself.